com.ryantenney.metrics.spring.config.annotation

Class MetricsConfigurationSupport

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ryantenney.metrics.spring.config.annotation.MetricsConfigurationSupport
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.context.annotation.ImportAware
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DelegatingMetricsConfiguration

    public class MetricsConfigurationSupport
extends Object
implements org.springframework.context.annotation.ImportAware
    This is the main class providing the configuration behind the Metrics Java config. It is typically imported by adding @EnableMetrics to an application @Configuration class.
    Since:
    3.0
    Author:
    Ryan Tenney
    See Also:
    MetricsConfigurer, MetricsConfigurerAdapter
